</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>火星探測衛星 Win 98 系統終升級，新軟件加快五倍探索時間</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/28/esawindows-98/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=esawindows-98</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[EMMA]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2022 10:29:31 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1107265</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>最近，歐洲太空總署（ESA）表示，其總署工程師正為火星探測衛星「火星快車」（Mars Express）更新所使 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>最近，歐洲太空總署（ESA）表示，其總署工程師正為火星探測衛星「火星快車」（Mars Express）更新所使用的 Windows 98 系統，期望更新能提升 19 年前發射的衛星的工作效率。</p><p>工程師 Carlo Nenna 表示，因軟件由 19 年前設計，並基於 Windows 98 所開發，在提高衛星的性能方面面臨許多挑戰，如成功更新將大幅提高衛星工作效率。歐洲太空總署指軟件將會由原本的 Windows 98 大幅升級至 ESA 全新重寫的 OS。新軟件會篩選及去除不必要的數據，取代原本容易快速耗盡記憶體的方案。</p><p>「火星快車」運營經理 Andrea Cicchetti 表示，新軟件可篩選不需要的數據，處理資料的能力加強，加快「火星快車」約五倍的時間進行探索，使其能更快、更廣泛分辨及研究星球表面，以確認火星新水源的所在地。</p><p>「火星快車」在 2018 年先後發送 5 張高清照片回地球，並合併出位處火星北部低地的「科羅廖夫坑」（Korolev crater）全貌，成為在火星上發現巨大地下液態水層的關鍵。</p><p>「火星快車」於 2003 年 6 月 2 日發射，內建的「火星地下和電離層探測高級雷達」（MARSIS）是基於 Microsoft 的 Windows 98 開發，但 Microsoft 早在 2016 年 7 月 11 日已停止支援 Windows 98。</p><p class="p1"><span class="s1">資料</span><span class="s2">來源：<a href="https://www.theverge.com/2022/6/24/23181715/mars-express-marsis-windows-98-upgrade-esa">theverge</a></span></p><p class="p2">—</p><p class="p2"><span class="s3">unwire.hk</span> Mewe <span class="s4">專頁：</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span class="s3">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl&amp;autoplay=0&amp;cc_load_policy=0&amp;cc_lang_pref=&amp;iv_load_policy=1&amp;loop=0&amp;modestbranding=1&amp;rel=0&amp;fs=1&amp;playsinline=1&amp;autohide=1&amp;theme=light&amp;color=white&amp;controls=0&amp;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><div class="feedflare">
<a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=dYXYTSmymRA:fMYekK_hEbI:yIl2AUoC8zA"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=yIl2AUoC8zA" border="0"></img></a> <a href="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?a=dYXYTSmymRA:fMYekK_hEbI:qj6IDK7rITs"><img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~ff/unwirelife?d=qj6IDK7rITs" border="0"></img></a>
</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>日本製 Okamura 人體工學電腦椅，滿足工作時人體支撐所需</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/06/28/okamurachair/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=okamurachair</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Tue, 28 Jun 2022 09:34:06 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[生活科技]]></category><category><![CDATA[Home Office]]></category><category><![CDATA[人體工學椅]]></category><category><![CDATA[健康]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1105382</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>今時今日好多人都會每日或者間中在家辨公，坐在電腦前有人會用普通凳， 但身體欠缺充足的支撐下容易疲倦、腰痠背痛， [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>今時今日好多人都會每日或者間中在家辨公，坐在電腦前有人會用普通凳， 但身體欠缺充足的支撐下容易疲倦、腰痠背痛，影響工作效率。到底如何選擇一張真正令你舒適工作的電腦椅是一門學問。今次會教大家一些考慮要點。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1106550 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-1-1.jpg" alt="" width="696" height="392" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-1-1.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-1-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0066-1-1-768x432.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 696px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105413" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0059-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2 class="CCgQ5 vCa9Yd QfkTvb MUxGbd v0nnCb" role="heading" aria-level="3">電競椅不是為工作而設計</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">懂買的人，是不會選電競椅作為長期工作的 office chair 之用，因為所謂電競椅基本上是賽車座椅，原意是包覆車手身體抵抗高速轉向時的引力，而且物料上也選用了防滑材質，這種特性是完全違反人體在工作時的身體所需，令你難於活動，更因為不通爽而出汗，所以緊記不要再犯這個錯誤。</p><h2>如何才是一張好的電腦椅</h2><p>我們在電腦前工作，因為要接觸鍵盤或滑鼠，身體坐姿多是坐直甚至微微向前傾，而且時常拿取電腦兩邊的文件或文具，因此一張好的電腦椅必需有足夠的承託力來支撐工作時的坐姿，還不要過份包覆身體阻礙活動。另外材質必需通爽透氣，在長時間工作下也能讓熱量或汗水快速排走。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">所以我們選購的第一條件，不是看它有多「包」住身體，而是腰部支撐是否足夠，調校的選項是否能讓用家調節到適合自己身體所需。綜合以上條件，今天小編介紹這系列擁有特別設計的日本製人體工學椅，看看能否合你眼緣。</p><h2>Okamura Contessa II 全面承託人體工學椅</h2><p style="font-weight: 400;">好多人會以為只要座椅夠大張就舒服，其實一張座椅最重要是設計夠好，不同坐姿都可以承託到身體容易疲倦的部位。<a href="https://www.shop.okamura-salotto.com.hk/contessa-seconda?lang=zh">Okamura Contessa Seconda (II) </a>的設計適合一般小型辦公室，或香港的狹窄家居，不但具有多項功能，為身體提供理想的承託能力，而且日本製的座椅強度甚高﹑持久耐用，正常使用下一般十年都毋須維修。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-14.20.53.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105407" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-14.20.53-643x580.jpg" alt="" width="643" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-14.20.53-643x580.jpg 643w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-14.20.53-768x693.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/螢幕截圖-2022-06-17-14.20.53.jpg 994w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 643px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Okamura Contessa II 的椅背採用了具伸縮性、耐用強度兼備的紗線，再結合觸感優良的柔軟網布製造（亦可選購皮革款式），網布擁有透氣特質，令用家更加舒適。另外，有別於一般辦公椅，它在手柄下方裝設按鈕調校椅背傾斜角度，一按就可調節理想角度，毋須在凳下左搵右搵。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0046.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105403" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0046-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0046-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0046-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0046.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105404" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0047.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲智能扶手的左右方設有調節按鈕，用作調校椅背傾斜角度、座椅高度，操作更為方便</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_comfort_main_chair_woman.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105397" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_comfort_main_chair_woman-552x580.png" alt="" width="552" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_comfort_main_chair_woman-552x580.png 552w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_comfort_main_chair_woman.png 623w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 552px" /></a></p><p>而且用家可調整椅背的傾斜張力，在較大張力時，用家甚至可讓身體放鬆慢慢向後躺，直至找到椅背的理想角度為止。</p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0044.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105416" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0044-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0044-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0044-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0044.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲用家可調節椅背傾斜的張力</p><p>用家可選擇固定的大型頭枕，或可調校角度的小型頭枕。大頭枕可以讓用家在椅上休息時，有更大面積承託頭部，而小型頭枕可調節角度，適合不同需要。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0021-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105398" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0021-1-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0021-1-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0021-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105399" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019-1-558x580.jpg" alt="" width="558" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019-1-558x580.jpg 558w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019-1-866x900.jpg 866w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019-1-768x798.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0019-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 558px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Okamura Contessa II 採用獨家研發技術，以三種不同柔軟度物料製造出多重硬度的坐墊：前方使用減輕大腿壓力的柔軟物質，後方就採用為支撐臀部重量而設，硬度較高的人造橡膠。另外椅座可前後調校，同樣適合用家不同坐姿。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0043.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105402" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0043-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0043-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0043-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0043.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Okamura Contessa II 另一特殊設計重點在它的「4D 扶手」，它可調節高度（幅度有 100mm）、扶手向內八字或向外八字角度（向內 15 度、向外 7.5 度），以至調節扶手前後與扶手闊窄。例如你需要辦公打字，手部承託不一定在桌面，而是可調高扶手，再調整闊窄，把手肘承託於座椅上，更為舒適；而當你靠後休息時，扶手可拉闊一點，再降低一點，以迎合你的休息姿勢。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0048.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105411" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0048-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0048-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0048-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0048.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0049.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105412" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0049-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0049-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0049-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0049.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>Okamura Sylphy 支援前傾的人體工學椅</h2><div><p>好多時打字或做功課，身體都會向前傾，此時再靚的椅背都沒有功用。而<span lang="EN-HK"><a href="https://www.shop.okamura-salotto.com.hk/sylphy?lang=zh"> Okamura Sylphy</a> </span>就有可前傾的椅背，加上可調節曲線背框、多重硬度坐墊及 <span lang="EN-HK">3D </span>扶手設計，讓用家在專心工作時都更為舒適。</p></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105393" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_-694x491.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="491" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_-694x491.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_-1273x900.jpg 1273w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_-768x543.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_-1536x1086.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/Sylphy_.jpg 1752w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">用家可選擇網背或軟墊背，背框帶有彎度調節功能，並可以向前傾（最大 10 度），讓背部支撐得更好，長時間工作都不會容易疲倦。當然它亦可後傾最大 23 度讓你靠後休息。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105408" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1-330x580.jpg" alt="" width="330" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1-330x580.jpg 330w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1-511x900.jpg 511w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1-768x1352.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1-873x1536.jpg 873w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1-1164x2048.jpg 1164w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0013-1.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 330px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;"><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-3.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105409" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-3-694x390.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-3-694x390.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-3-768x432.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0011-3.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a>▲頭枕後方更可加入褸架配件</p><div><p><span lang="EN-HK">Okamura Sylphy </span>的背框可以調節弧度，調節至較細弧度時，便能夠更緊貼地包覆用家的臀部與腰部，提供更好的承託力，特別適合身形較矯小的女士們。</p></div><div><p><span lang="EN-HK">Okamura Sylphy </span>的多重硬度坐墊同樣使用三段不同柔軟度的物料製造，前方的柔軟部分，不會影響腿部血液循環，後方較硬的部分就適合支撐臀部及身體重量。椅座同樣可前後調整，適合不同身高的用家。</p></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-2.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105410" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-2-694x537.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="537" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-2-694x537.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-2-1164x900.jpg 1164w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-2-768x594.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0012-2.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">椅背採用網布材料，有助透氣。同時亦可加配承託脊骨的腰靠組件，可以取代一般常用的腰墊，不需犧牲坐位空間，而且背靠還可調節高低，達致更有效的脊骨承託效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" class=" wp-image-1106553 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/132516262.jpg" alt="" width="690" height="388" /></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">3D 扶手設計可調整高度（最大上下 100mm）﹑前後（幅度為 50mm）及角度（向內或向外 20 度），適合不同工作場合，讓手部有更舒適承託。</p><h2>Okamura Cynara 全網精緻多功能辦公椅</h2><div><p>如果家居不適合放置大型座椅，或者會議室需要配置數量較多的座椅，設計簡潔而輕盈的<a href="https://www.shop.okamura-salotto.com.hk/cynara?lang=zh"><span lang="EN-HK"> Okamura Cynara </span></a>就能讓用家在較細的座椅上，擁有最舒適的乘坐感受。</p></div><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105395" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02-694x484.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="484" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02-694x484.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02-1280x893.jpg 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02-768x536.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02-1536x1072.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_scene02.jpg 2000w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire0032.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class=" wp-image-1106555 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire00368682.jpg" alt="" width="696" height="443" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire00368682.jpg 1132w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire00368682-694x441.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/unwire00368682-768x488.jpg 768w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 696px" /></a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">Cynara 設計簡約，特別適合簡約風的辦公室或家居。即使它用途極似「開會凳」，但就擁有椅背角度調節功能，細小的調節杆，可控制椅背由直立至靠後傾斜最大 12 度。另外椅背同坐位部份都採用了通風優良的網布，可輕鬆支撐用家的身體。其空心椅輪與多款顏色選擇，令它成為時尚之選。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_characteristics02.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1105390" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_characteristics02-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_characteristics02-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_characteristics02-120x120.jpg 120w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/06/img_characteristics02.jpg 720w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></a></p><h2>總結：人體工學辦公椅舒適度大有不同</h2><div><p>小編辦公室內的座椅未有特別講究，而今次就親身體會到這類看似設計相似，但功能各有不同，而且各個部位可調角度闊度，例如椅背、頭枕、座墊，以至手柄等等，調節到最適合自己的體型與坐姿，效果甚至比起大大張的座椅、電競椅更加好。大家在選購家居電腦椅、辦公室座椅時，都可以考慮一下這類人體工學椅。</p></div><p>讀者可直接在 e-shop 查看更多及選購：<a href="https://www.shop.okamura-salotto.com.hk/?lang=zh">連結按此</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><iframe style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;" id="_ytid_84661" width="590" height="332" data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/?enablejsapi=1&amp;list=PLiEPZioiGtHw